title: Phone Roulette: We call random people and tell embarrassing stories
description: Falen had a new idea for a bit called Phone Roulette where we have to scroll through our contacts on our phone and whoever it lands on, we have to call and tell them an embarrassing story about ourselves.  It's hilarious for anyone listening but so terrifying for the person calling!
